{"tid":2440637,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"粉絲哀號！女優群起退追蹤　一劍浣春秋：太多人傳下體照","createTime":"2021-03-10T05:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T07:52:42.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"40929fa67b146e68367de119682c726465128383","tid":2440637,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:51:45.000Z","msg":"你有用twitter追蹤AV女優嗎？AV評論家一劍浣春秋指出，有些女優只要你追蹤她，對方就會反追蹤回來，就算平常只發廢文，女優也不見得看懂中文，但有人在網路上默默關心你，那感覺還是挺不賴，沒想到最近某些女優將追蹤的粉絲全部刪光！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/10/3058387-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F10%2F3058387-PH.jpg&h=191751c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲小倉由菜解釋退追蹤的原因。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n一劍浣春秋表示，包括跨足Youtuber的小倉由菜、聲勢不錯的新人早野詩在內，均解除了所有粉絲的追蹤，讓有些粉絲不太開心，就像臉書被刪好友一樣莫名其妙，有的粉絲認為被女優追蹤是種肯定，突然被退追蹤自然不太高興，站在經營粉絲團的角度，這實在不是聰明的做法，為什麼女優要這麼做呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/10/3058389-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F10%2F3058389-PH.jpg&h=4b617ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲小倉由菜解釋退追蹤的原因。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n小倉由菜為此發文解釋，她是為了「公平」二字，因為影迷是愛比較的生物，追了一個沒追另一個，不只彼此之間容易爭吵，有時還會鬧到她那裡，倒不如全都解除一勞永逸，如果是真心的粉絲，想必不會計較。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/10/3058390-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F10%2F3058390-PH.jpg&h=ab890829&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲小倉由菜解釋退追蹤的原因。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n一劍浣春秋點出另一個原因，有些粉絲被女優追蹤後，也不知道在想什麼，居然傳自己下體照片過去獻寶，女優索性通通解除追蹤，然後關閉對陌生人的私訊功能，藉以解決這類問題。<br />\n<br />\n一劍浣春秋認為，兩個理由她都能接受，但兩個理由可能不被粉絲接受，掉粉是可以預見的結果，只能說經營粉絲很不容易，沒人追蹤最悽慘，有人追蹤也會有煩惱，只好採取全員退追的方式處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/10/3058388-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F10%2F3058388-PH.jpg&h=8aefa503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲小倉由菜解釋退追蹤的原因。（圖／翻攝自推特）"},{"pid":"65019cf396dd9e2e0bd0d81416e8a0bb9e3ddf59","tid":2440637,"uid":232748,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:53:05.000Z","msg":"下體圖呢？"},{"pid":"49880c0c6ddc521a7b8f8f4b626f13932d2554f5","tid":2440637,"uid":24570,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65019cf396dd9e2e0bd0d81416e8a0bb9e3ddf59","tid":2440637,"uid":232748,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:53:05.000Z","msg":"下體圖呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"想睇J?"},{"pid":"ba6766635495984b38c364c6b40dbb98716eac5f","tid":2440637,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65019cf396dd9e2e0bd0d81416e8a0bb9e3ddf59","tid":2440637,"uid":232748,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:53:05.000Z","msg":"下體圖呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"男人下體圖wo...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64869a4d02a2830e8368ae886462858edc279500","tid":2440637,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65019cf396dd9e2e0bd0d81416e8a0bb9e3ddf59","tid":2440637,"uid":232748,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:53:05.000Z","msg":"下體圖呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:56:07.000Z","msg":"證明你係下體諗野"},{"pid":"904b7a21a61298f90a695eec6a04aea339ebee37","tid":2440637,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:56:13.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 正正經經去叫隻雞啦"},{"pid":"e84891113aea224feacc83324ff97a777f5d2964","tid":2440637,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"904b7a21a61298f90a695eec6a04aea339ebee37","tid":2440637,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:56:13.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 正正經經去叫隻雞啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:58:21.000Z","msg":"尊重三文魚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b59d7c7115b4f24b977c6b07260